                  <div class="why-card" style="text-align:left; padding:40px;">
                    <div class="icon-box" style="margin-bottom:20px;">📋</div>
                    <h3>1. Medical Trip Planning</h3>
                    <p>We analyze your medical needs, recommend the best hospitals and doctors, schedule appointments, and create a complete itinerary. We also provide visa guidance and travel documentation support.</p>
                    <div style="margin-top:12px; font-size:0.85rem; color:var(--gray-600);"><strong>Fee:</strong> Free consultation</div>
                  </div>
