                    <div class="icon-box" style="margin-bottom:20px; background:var(--coral);">📅</div>
                    <h3>2. Online Appointment Booking Service</h3>
                    <p style="max-width:600px; margin:12px auto;">Share your medical condition with us, and we will help you book an appointment with a Chinese-speaking doctor online. You can visit the hospital on your own and communicate with the doctor using translation apps.</p>
                    <div class="booking-form" style="margin-top:24px; text-align:left;">
